name: The Great Warrior of the Luo

metadata.name: Luanda Magere: The Great Warrior of the Luo
metadata.description:
Luanda Magere, the Luo's Great Warrior was born in the year 1720 to Abonyo Wuod Omolo and mother Nyabera. No Luo Warrior has had a greater impact on the community than Luanda Magere, the Sidho clan's son. His name means "fierce rock" or "rock that builds," indicating how powerful the warrior once was.

This motion portrait from the series “The Great Warrior of the Luo” features the legendary Luo warrior Luanda Magere.

Format: 1080 × 1920 video.
